title: Could the remains of a 'dead' comet still be in the solar system? Astronomers are still searching 6 years later
description: The fate of a comet that was predicted to pass close to Earth remains a mystery five years after its dramatic breakup in the inner solar system.
content: The fate of a comet that was predicted to pass close to Earth remains a mystery five years after its dramatic breakup in the inner solar system.
